      <title>哈克：沙特欢迎油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/haque-saudi-would-welcome-higher-oil-prices-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋国民银行首席经济学家兼研究主管 Khatija Haque 表示，沙特阿拉伯欢迎油价上涨。她补充说，由于中国需求疲软，她预计 OPEC+ 不会放松减产。Khatija Haque 还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了沙特阿拉伯的经济前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/haque-saudi-would-welcome-higher-oil-prices-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞机停飞导致 Wizz Air 利润下滑，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/wizz-air-shares-sink-as-aircraft-groundings-cut-into-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wizz Air Holdings Plc 下调了今年的利润预测，导致其股价出现自疫情以来的最大跌幅，因为这家廉价航空公司在繁忙的夏季旅游季节面临着飞机停飞的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/wizz-air-shares-sink-as-aircraft-groundings-cut-into-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行汽车业务业绩不佳，欧洲股市小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汽车行业和法国兴业银行的一系列业绩令人失望，欧洲股市因此下跌。这让美联储可能在下个月降息的迹象黯然失色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自四月以来，石油交易商增持了大部分中东风险期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/oil-traders-load-up-on-most-options-since-april-on-mideast-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势加剧，增加了油价飙升的可能性，石油交易商纷纷买入看涨期权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/oil-traders-load-up-on-most-options-since-april-on-mideast-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦证券交易所集团首席执行官称 IPO 计划“令人鼓舞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/lse-group-ceo-says-ipo-pipeline-encouraging-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦证券交易所集团首席执行官戴维·施维默 (David Schwimmer) 讨论了收益、IPO 和与微软的合作关系。他在彭博电视上表示，首次公开募股的前景“令人鼓舞，而且情况还在不断改善。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/lse-group-ceo-says-ipo-pipeline-encouraging-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:08:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特顶级化工企业盈利超出预期，呈现反弹迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/top-saudi-chemical-firm-beats-profit-estimate-in-sign-of-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯最大的化学公司第二季度的利润超过了分析师的预期，这是一个早期迹象，表明该行业在经历艰难的低迷后可能正在复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/top-saudi-chemical-firm-beats-profit-estimate-in-sign-of-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
