    <item>
      <title>宝马盈利因中国主要市场需求疲软而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 第二季度盈利出现下滑，原因是其主要市场中国销量下滑，这家德国公司加入了越来越多面临需求放缓困境的汽车制造商的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行盈利超预期，瞄准顶级 FICC 角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-investment-bank-outperforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 公布的第二季度利润超过分析师预期，原因是交易员和交易员表现出色，且该银行开始看到法国加息带来的延迟效益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-investment-bank-outperforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:53:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
